# -----------------------------
# Credentials & real account data
# -----------------------------
# "GPN Account.xlsx" / "GPN Account - ERP.xlsx" are DATAPROVIDER-mode account
# fixtures — each row is [companyUser, companyPass, userUser, userPass] for a
# real customer account, i.e. plaintext credentials, not synthetic test data.
# Never commit these; supply them at runtime instead (Jenkins file
# credential, a Docker/K8s volume mount, or a local copy kept outside git).
"src/test/resources/GPN Account.xlsx"
"src/test/resources/GPN Account - ERP.xlsx"

# .env.gpn holds resolved ALFADOCK_*_USER/PASS values for local docker-compose
# runs — real secrets, must never be committed.
.env.gpn

